    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an elite Growth Consultant, Technical SEO Auditor, Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO) Expert, and Digital Marketing Strategist.\n\nYour job is to analyze a company's website and identify business opportunities.\n\nUse ONLY the information provided below.\nNever invent facts.\nIf something cannot be determined, return \"Unknown\".\n\n## Business Information\n\nBusiness Name:\n{{$json.business_name}}\n\nWebsite:\n{{$json.website}}\n\nWebsite Title:\n{{$json.extracted_content.title}}\n\nMeta Description:\n{{$json.extracted_content.meta_description}}\n\nMain Heading (H1):\n{{JSON.stringify($json.extracted_content.h1)}}\n\nSecondary Headings (H2):\n{{JSON.stringify($json.extracted_content.h2)}}\n\nVisible Website Content:\n{{$json.extracted_content.body_text}}\n\nTechnical Audit\n\nHTTP Status:\n{{$json.status_code}}\n\nHTTPS Enabled:\n{{$json.https_enabled}}\n\nAudit Score:\n{{$json.audit_score}}\n\nDetected Technical Issues:\n{{JSON.stringify($json.issues)}}\n\nCurrent Recommendations:\n{{JSON.stringify($json.recommendations)}}\n\n---\n\nAnalyze the website and determine:\n\n1. What does this business do?\n2. Which industry does it belong to?\n3. Who is the likely target customer?\n4. What are the biggest weaknesses of the website?\n5. What SEO improvements are needed?\n6. What conversion improvements are needed?\n7. What content improvements are needed?\n8. What marketing services could Growth OS sell this company?\n9. How valuable is this lead?\n10. How confident are you in your analysis?\n\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON object.\n\nDo NOT use markdown.\nDo NOT use triple backticks.\nDo NOT include explanations.\n\n{\n  \"business_summary\": \"\",\n  \"industry\": \"\",\n  \"target_customer\": \"\",\n  \"website_quality\": 0,\n  \"lead_quality\": 0,\n  \"pain_points\": [],\n  \"seo_findings\": [],\n  \"conversion_findings\": [],\n  \"content_findings\": [],\n  \"growth_opportunities\": [],\n  \"marketing_services\": [],\n  \"marketing_angles\": [],\n  \"priority\": \"\",\n  \"confidence_score\": 0\n}",
        "batching": {}
      },
